- Alan is Cynthia's ancestor → Alan > Cynthia

**Tracing Elijah forward (toward descendants):**
- Elijah is Harold's ancestor → Elijah > Harold
- Harold is Michael's ancestor → Harold > Michael
- And this chain continues down through all the same people listed above to Brandon

**The complete chain is:**
Elijah > Harold > Michael > Bobby > Philip > Ralph > Karen > Denise > Patricia > Mason > Diana > Amy > Gabriel > Dorothy > Andrea > Mary > Kathleen > Brian > Madison > Pamela > Kevin > William > Tyler > Carl > Danielle > Brenda > Heather > Jerry > Ruth > Mark > Logan > George > Vincent > Margaret > Zachary > Kelly > Jennifer > Richard > Bryan > Ryan > Christine > Janice > Stephen > Charles > Melissa > Jeffrey > Abigail > Albert > Sandra > Rachel > Justin > Teresa > Janet > Arthur > Amanda > Lawrence > Alice > Megan > Alan > Cynthia > Samantha > Beverly > Robert > Brandon

Since Elijah appears at the beginning of this chain and Brandon at the end, **Brandon is Elijah's descendant**.
